ELK FOr SE-Application.com


1. Check index name in the logstash .conf and create index in the elastic search

2. Run logstash with new conf =   bin/logstash -f logstash.conf

3. For Every Change to take effect , restart elastic search and kiabana


4. GET _cluster/health

5. get information about cluster = GET _NODES/STATS


6. create an Index = PUT Indes_Name = PUT SE-Application

7. ELK Cluster Security =  User Authentication & Encrypted Communication


